      "writtenOn": "2026-04-30T16:17:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Specifically, it uses the JGit matching engine. \nLike:-\nSupported: refs/heads/* (matches all branches)\nSupported: refs/tags/* (matches all tags)\nSupported: refs/heads/feature-* (matches all feature branches)\nUnsupported: refs/*/master (wildcards in the middle are generally not supported in standard Git refspecs).",
